title: GET_ENTITY_POPULATION_TYPE
content:
0xFC30DDFF// GetEntityPopulationType
int GET_ENTITY_POPULATION_TYPE(Entity entity);Parameters:entity: the entity to obtain the population type fromReturns: Returns the population type ID, defined by the below enumeration:`cpp
enum ePopulationType
{
	POPTYPE_UNKNOWN = 0,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PERMANENT,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PARKED,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PATROL,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_SCENARIO,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_AMBIENT,
	POPTYPE_PERMANENT,
	POPTYPE_MISSION,
	POPTYPE_REPLAY,
	POPTYPE_CACHE,
	POPTYPE_TOOL
};This native gets an entity's population type.
